{"tid":2185240,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"羅卓堯：每當專家提相反意見　便被標籤成反中央反政府","createTime":"2020-09-02T06:37:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T07:08:18.000Z","uid":79563,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"073af6d6ef41fde0ccbedad06e706ab101dfa7aa","tid":2185240,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T06:37:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1547369-20200902.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1547369-20200902.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=5n7Vw74FaX2H6oE8X5RxXD632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=1dc20317\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1547369-20200902.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=4148f7b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1547369-20200902.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n醫管局員工陣線副主席羅卓堯批評，政府以政治凌駕專業意見或公共衛生領域，專家或專業團隊提出與政府相反的意見，或是提出改善意見，便引來政府很大反彈，標籤成反中央及反政府，以敵對態度應對意見，不檢視普及社區檢測計劃有何不足便推行。<br />\n<br />\n羅卓堯在本台節目《千禧年代》說，現時本港政府有「國家隊」的資源，應將資源用在值得使用的地方，又指政府及建制派多次扭曲他們所說「封關」的意思，用「封關」這詞語可令市民相對簡單地理解，但所說的不是不容許貨物進入香港，也非不准港人回港。"},{"pid":"493d8d0d28c53a88553fefbad0e878f15fa1c20e","tid":2185240,"uid":96327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T06:38:19.000Z","msg":"十二位手足被扣押第九日 務必繼續關注聲援<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2184284\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2184284</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"64c00c81284ac342b353dbd765baf86e98498b8e","tid":2185240,"uid":346260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T06:39:42.000Z","msg":"有用 post ,樓主可唔可以置頂？唔該曬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係想保護自己同身邊嘅人？即刻入嚟睇吓!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets